FBIS4-46412 "jptot024__l94089" JPRS-TOT-94-024-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 9 June 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA LEBANON Hizballah Kidnaps Seven Linked to al-Dirani Abduction Hizballah Kidnaps Seven Linked to al-Dirani Abduction `Emgergency Battalion' Used NC0906075994 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 0700 GMT 9 Jun 94 NC0906075994 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] Gunmen from the subversive organization Hizballah kidnapped six Lebanese and a retired Syrian soldier in the Ba'labakk area last night. It has been learned that members of the so-called Emergency Battalion [katibat al-tawari'] of Hizballah kidnapped three of them from their homes after mistreating them. They kidnapped the other four in public places. Lebanese and Syrian security agencies are holding contacts with Hizballah to seek the release of the those kidnapped.
